        given-names: Harika
      - family-names: Urban
        given-names: Lara
    journal: "GigaScience"
    year: 2025
    doi: 10.1093/gigascience/giaf100

  - type: article
    title: >
      Rapid avian influenza profiling using the latest nanopore sequencing
